'''Diggil-ej''' is a former [[week]]ly [[radio]] [[radio programming|program]] on [[Sweden]]'s [[SR Atlas]] [[digital radio]] station. It was broadcast on Wednesdays at 21.00 [[Central European Time|CET]] and was hosted by [[Kris Boswell]] and featured a collection of [[Eurovision Song Contest]] related [[songs]].

