'''''Drakarna över Helsingfors''''' (''Kites over Helsingfors)''<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.booksfromfinland.fi/1996/09/a-day-in-the-life/|title = Kjell Westö: Kites over Helsingfors|last =|first =|date =|website = Books from Finland|publisher =|access-date = 2016-07-31}}</ref> is a Swedish-language novel written by Finnish author [[Kjell Westö]]. The book tells about the life and faiths of the Bexar family, a [[Swedish-speaking Finns|Swedish-speaking]] [[Finland|Finnish]] family living in [[Helsinki]] (''Helsingfors'' in Swedish), from the 1960s to the 1990s.
